<HEAD>Israeli Group Says April 2nd Bloodiest Month of Uprising</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS throughout to UPDATE with 15 wounded, report that PLO
officials abroad approve most orders to kill collaborators. No pickup.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By G.G. LaBELLE</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>JERUSALEM (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
